Can also be tested with something like this (on `clang++  -O0` arm64):

```cpp
#include <array>
int main() {
  using A = std::array<unsigned char, 33>;
  A obj{};
  A copy{std::move(obj)};
  obj = std::move(obj); // valid, but unspecified state
  obj = std::move(copy);
}
```
